# Personal Info

## Basic

- **Name (zh):** 你的中文名
- **Name (en):** Your English Name
- **Location:** City, Country
- **Tagline:** A one-line summary of your professional identity (e.g., "ML Engineer with 5 years of NLP experience")

## Contact

- **Email:** your@email.com
- **Phone:** +1 xxx xxx xxxx
- **GitHub:** your-github-username
- **LinkedIn:** https://www.linkedin.com/in/your-profile/
- **Personal site:** https://yoursite.com (optional)
- **Portfolio:** https://portfolio.example.com (optional)

<!--
Tips:
- Include both zh and en names if you apply to jobs in both languages
- Phone format: use international format with country code
- LinkedIn URL: use your custom URL if you have one
- Only include links you want on your resume
-->
